snippet.title: The Iron Oath - Turn-based Tactical Rpg - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
THE IRON OATH is a #turnbased game set in a dark-fantasy world where the main component is the tactics and management of the guild in a dynamic world that varies according to our choices.

STEAM PAGE: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/699330/The_Iron_Oath
